  "detailed_description": "It is a 2D adventure game with cute characters.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe stage is a mini-game with a total of 7 stages.<br />\r\nThere are videos at the opening and ending.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe atmosphere is mysterious, cute, and hand-drawn.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n------------<br />\r\nSummary of the story.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe mother's soul, who died in the accident, was reborn as a defective doll in a doll factory.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe defective doll with the mother's soul is about to return to her daughter.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease help her get to her daughter safely.<br />\r\nPlease help me to get her home safely.",
